er p\u00e5 ofrene og de etterlatte, og jeg h\u00e5per vi kan v\u00e6re sammen om \u00e5 ford\u00f8mme all slags type ekstremisme, og bevege oss sammen mot en bedre framtid.", "Det er nok n\u00e5."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "meninger"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "aed1affef708eff30a26f11a520741347bfe16b448f6c990cb0ce266f5c6a16e"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-07-15T16:29:45.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "I dag er det stille i Nice. Noen bader, turister trasker rundt i gamlebyen, men latteren og de h\u00f8ylytte samtalene jeg har blitt vant til den siste uken h\u00f8res ikke."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/meninger/article13045447.ece/jfsee5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/tb40c5d6.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/a5228f63ee6bc28b7975b6629ca5da75651baaf5.jpg?58e7b320"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Vi m\u00e5 sammen ford\u00f8mme all slags ekstremisme -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "a5228f63ee6bc28b7975b6629ca5da75651baaf5"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["Terror i Nice", "frankrike"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "Terror i Nice,frankrike"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "meninger"}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "travel"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["ekstremisme", "f\u00f8le", "ford\u00f8mme all", "all slags", "ford\u00f8mme all slags", "angrep"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["le m\u00e8ridien", "ut\u00f8ya", "middelhavet", "charlie"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["europa", "nice", "paris"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-sentiment", "value": "negative"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": "meninger"}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/meninger/article13045447.ece/jfsee5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/tb40c5d6.jpg"}, {"fie